  "texts": [
    "Due to my heart failure and atrial fibrillation, I have to be careful with my heart rate and monitor it regularly.\"",
    "When silicon participants were asked about their physical activity levels, their detailed reply included their age, health conditions, living conditions, and reduced physical activity.",
    "To other questions, they provided insights about their limited physical capabilities, emphasizing the need for caution due to specific health concerns.",
    "Our study found that GPT-3.5 primarily used explicit context information provided in the prompts, such as age, gender, comorbidities, and residency, in its responses.",
    "It showed less proficiency in inferring and using backstory details not directly provided and did not infer details such as retirement."
  ]
}